<span class='communityAnswerText'>
<span class="expandableContainer"><span class="truncatedContent">I dont think he made himself into a chair but fused himself and made one with the chair. If he turned into a chair there would be two chairs the &quot;orig<a class="jsShow showAction" href="#">…more</a></span><span class="fullContent">I dont think he made himself into a chair but fused himself and made one with the chair. If he turned into a chair there would be two chairs the "original" and him.<br />I thought it was so sad how she begs him to only use that one chair so she could always know where he is. I almost cried.<a class="jsHide hideAction" href="#">(less)</a></span></span>
