<div id="review_3784100650" class="review nosyndicate" itemprop="reviews" itemscope itemtype="http://schema.org/Review">
  <link itemprop="url" href="https://www.goodreads.com/review/show/3784100650" />
    <a title="Debbie" class="left imgcol" href="/user/show/41918078-debbie"><img alt="Debbie" src="https://images.gr-assets.com/users/1594390250p2/41918078.jpg" /></a>

  <div class="left bodycol">
    <div class="reviewHeader uitext stacked">
        <a class="reviewDate createdAt right" href="/review/show/3784100650?book_show_action=true">Apr 03, 2021</a>

      <span itemprop="author" itemscope itemtype="http://schema.org/Person">
        <a title="Debbie" class="user" itemprop="url" name="Debbie" href="/user/show/41918078-debbie">Debbie</a>
      </span>

        rated it
        <span class=" staticStars notranslate" title="really liked it"><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10">really liked it</span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p0"></span></span>

          <span class="greyText">&nbsp;&middot;&nbsp;</span>
          <a class="lightGreyText" title="Audiobook 9780307737144" href="/book/show/9822996-the-particular-sadness-of-lemon-cake">review of another edition</a>


        

          <div class="uitext greyText bookshelves">
            Shelves:
              <a class="actionLinkLite" href="/review/list/41918078-debbie?shelf=2021-reads">2021-reads</a>, 
              <a class="actionLinkLite" href="/review/list/41918078-debbie?shelf=audiobook">audiobook</a>, 
              <a class="actionLinkLite" href="/review/list/41918078-debbie?shelf=contemporary-fiction">contemporary-fiction</a>, 
              <a class="actionLinkLite" href="/review/list/41918078-debbie?shelf=magical-realism">magical-realism</a>, 
              <a class="actionLinkLite" href="/review/list/41918078-debbie?shelf=young-adult">young-adult</a>, 
              <a class="actionLinkLite" href="/review/list/41918078-debbie?shelf=food">food</a>
          </div>
    </div>


        <div class="reviewText stacked">
              <span id="reviewTextContainer3784100650" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer14333075619664101595">The Edelstein family seems &quot;normal&quot; to outsiders, but the dysfunction of each family member makes up the gist of this story with Rose, the youngest, caught in the middle, especially when just before her 9th birthday, she learns that she possesses a &quot;gift&quot;. Throughout the story, she learns how to understand, how to cope within her family and its secrets.<br/><br/>Sometimes I sympathized with Rose, and sometimes she annoyed me, but as I kept listening, I began to understand why she did (or didn&apos;t) do the th</span>
  <span id="freeText14333075619664101595" style="display:none">The Edelstein family seems "normal" to outsiders, but the dysfunction of each family member makes up the gist of this story with Rose, the youngest, caught in the middle, especially when just before her 9th birthday, she learns that she possesses a "gift". Throughout the story, she learns how to understand, how to cope within her family and its secrets.<br /><br />Sometimes I sympathized with Rose, and sometimes she annoyed me, but as I kept listening, I began to understand why she did (or didn't) do the things she did. I also learned why her dad was so detached, why her mom tried so hard to understand her children, and what was up with her brother, Joseph.<br /><br />Author <a href="https://www.goodreads.com/author/show/5285.Aimee_Bender" title="Aimee Bender" rel="nofollow noopener">Aimee Bender</a>, who also narrates this audiobook, kept me hanging right to the end. I found it thought-provoking and heartbreaking. Don't expect a "happily ever after" ending - such an ending would have been an extreme disappointment to this story.<br /><br />Interesting read!</span>
  <a data-text-id="14333075619664101595" href="#" onclick="swapContent($(this));; return false;">...more</a>

          </span>
        </div>


