      <div id="aboutAuthor" class=" clearFloats bigBox"><div class="h2Container gradientHeaderContainer"><h2 class="brownBackground"><a href="/author/show/5285.Aimee_Bender">About Aimee Bender</a></h2></div><div class="bigBoxBody"><div class="bigBoxContent containerWithHeaderContent">
          <div class='bookAuthorProfile'>
<div class='bookAuthorProfile__topContainer'>
<div class='bookAuthorProfile__photoContainer'>
<a href="/author/show/5285.Aimee_Bender"><div class='bookAuthorProfile__photo' style='background-image: url(https://images.gr-assets.com/authors/1291155858p3/5285.jpg);'></div>
</a></div>
<div class='bookAuthorProfile__widgetContainer'>
<div class='bookAuthorProfile__name'>
<a href="/author/show/5285.Aimee_Bender">Aimee Bender
</a></div>
<div class='goodreadsAuthorBadge'></div>
<div class='bookAuthorProfile__followerCount'>
2,029
followers
</div>

</div>
</div>
<div class='bookAuthorProfile__about'>

<span id="freeTextContainer2988971387632277297"><b> Aimee Bender </b> is the author of the novel <i>An Invisible Sign of My Own</i> and of the collections <i>The Girl in the Flammable Skirt</i> and <i>Willful Creatures</i>. Her work has been widely anthologized and has been translated into ten languages. She lives in Los Angeles.</span>

</div>
</div>

<div class="clear"></div></div></div><div class="bigBoxBottom"></div></div>

  

